name: mapreduce.jobhistory.datestring.cache.size
explanation: The negative value of the mapreduce.jobhistory.datestring.cache.size configuration option could be causing the issue. This value should be a positive integer representing the size of the date string cache.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.resource.cpu-vcores
explanation: The number of virtual CPU cores the MR AppMaster needs is set to 1. This might be insufficient for the task, causing the speculation.

name: yarn.nodemanager.log-aggregation.roll-monitoring-interval-seconds.min
explanation: The description for this configuration option is missing. This could be causing issues with the log aggregation roll monitoring interval.
